highway=bus_stop
bus=yes
public_transport=platform
name=*
ref=*
local_ref=*
shelter=*
passenger_information_display=*
bench=*
bin=*

naptan:verified=no deleted on verification
source=naptan_import;survey

Not physically present, not used

   physically_present=no
   [and remove highway=bus_stop]

Not physically present, used

   physically_present=no
   highway=bus_stop

NaPTAN mapping

AlternativeDescriptors naptan:AltTYPE=* (and AlternativeDescriptors.CommonName -> alt_name)
AtcoCode 	           naptan:AtcoCode=*
Bearing                naptan:Bearing=*
CommonName             naptan:CommonName=* name=*[1]
Crossing               naptan:Crossing=*
Indicator              naptan:Indicator=* (parsed value in local_ref=*[1])
Landmark               naptan:Landmark=*
NaptanCode             naptan:NaptanCode=* and ref=*[1]
Notes                  naptan:Notes=*
ShortCommonName        naptan:ShortCommonName=*
Street                 naptan:Street=*
Type                   nptan:BusStopType=*

[1] Only when 'actively' converting the data